---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '11 March 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Killawot"
  description="Privacy policy for Killawot. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-10 text-gray-300">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            Killawot is an AI automation and software consultancy based in Bristol, UK.
            You can contact us at <a href="mailto:info@killawot.com" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">info@killawot.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">What data we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-white">Contact form</strong> — When you submit the contact form we collect your name, email address, company (optional), and message. This data is used solely to respond to your enquiry.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-white">Analytics (with consent)</strong> — If you accept cookies, we use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymised usage data: pages visited, time on site, approximate location (country/city), device type, and referral source. This helps us improve the site. No personally identifiable information is collected via analytics.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We only set analytics cookies if you explicitly accept them via the cookie banner. If you decline, no cookies are set.</p>
          <p>Analytics cookies set by Google Analytics 4:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside text-gray-400">
            <li><code class="text-gray-300">_ga</code> — distinguishes users, expires after 2 years</li>
            <li><code class="text-gray-300">_ga_*</code> — maintains session state, expires after 2 years</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">You can change your preference at any time by clearing your browser's local storage or cookies for this site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">How we use your data</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-1 list-disc list-inside text-gray-400">
            <li>To respond to enquiries submitted via the contact form</li>
            <li>To understand how visitors use the site and improve its content (analytics, consent-only)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-400">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Resend</strong> — processes contact form submissions to deliver email notifications to us. <a href="https://resend.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">Resend privacy policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Google Analytics 4</strong> — used for site analytics with your consent. Data is processed by Google. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">Google privacy policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Cloudflare</strong> — hosts and delivers this website. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">Cloudflare privacy policy</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data retention</h2>
          <p>Contact form emails are retained in our inbox and reviewed as needed. We do not maintain a separate database of enquiries. Analytics data is retained per Google Analytics' default 14-month data retention period.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Under UK GDPR you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1 list-disc list-inside text-gray-400">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to processing</li>
            <li>Lodge a complaint with the <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">ICO</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:info@killawot.com" class="text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors">info@killawot.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected in the "last updated" date above.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
